.code-review-graph/

# ⚠️ 安全：额外的敏感文件保护
# 避免意外提交包含密钥的文件
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
*.secret
credentials.json
*.credentials
auth.json

# IDE 的临时配置
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace
